In the following PowerShell code, functions hour00_numbers and hour01_numbers create two arrays, that contain numbers matching a specific regex.
function hour00_numbers {
    foreach ($event in $filter00) {
        $hour00Numbers = @()
        $hour00Numbers += [regex]::Matches($event.Source.Summary -replace ' ', '9 *[45679]( *[0-9]){6}').Value
