AnswerBody:
For your case, you can simply wrap the payload from client in a $map to convert them into ObjectIds with $toObjectId
db.store.aggregate([
  {
    $match: {
      $expr: {
        "$in": [
          "$id",
          {
            "$map": {
              // your payload from client here
              "input": [
                "63da2f1f7662144569f78ddd",
                "63da2f1f7662144569f78ddb",
                "63da2f1f7662144569f78dda"
              ],
              "as": "id",
              "in": {
                "$toObjectId": "$$id"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  {
